            <div style="margin-top: 12px;">
              <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;">라이선스 서버 URL</label>
              <input type="text" id="licenseServerUrl" placeholder="https://script.google.com/macros/s/..." 
                style="width: 100%; padding: 10px 14px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s;" 
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" onblur="this.style.borderColor='#e2e8f0'">
              <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 6px;">기본 서버가 설정되어 있습니다. 변경이 필요한 경우만 입력하세요.</p>
          </div>
          </details>

          <!-- 라이선스 코드 (우선) -->
          <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea15 0%, #764ba215 100%); border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid #667eea;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: 700; color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 15px;">
              📋 라이선스 코드 (신규 등록)
            </label>
            <input type="text" id="licenseCode" placeholder="XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX" maxlength="19" 
              style="width: 100%; padding: 14px 18px; border: 2px solid #667eea; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: monospace; letter-spacing: 3px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700;" 
              onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#764ba2'; this.style.boxShadow='0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1)'" 
              onblur="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'; this.style.boxShadow='none'" 
              oninput="formatLicenseCode(this)">
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px;">
              <input type="text" id="licenseUserId2" placeholder="아이디" 
                style="flex: 1; padding: 10px 14px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s;" 
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" onblur="this.style.borderColor='#e2e8f0'">
              <input type="password" id="licenseUserPassword2" placeholder="비밀번호" 
                style="flex: 1; padding: 10px 14px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s;" 
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" onblur="this.style.borderColor='#e2e8f0'">
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5;">
              💡 코드와 함께 아이디/비밀번호를 입력하면, 다음부터는 아이디/비밀번호만으로 로그인 가능합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">또는</div>

          <!-- 아이디/비밀번호 로그인 (기존 사용자) -->
          <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;">
            <label style="display: block; font-weight: 700; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 15px;">
              👤 아이디/비밀번호 로그인 (기존 사용자)
            </label>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
              <input type="text" id="licenseUserId" placeholder="아이디" 
                style="width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 14px; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s;" 
                onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" onblur="this.style.borderColor='#e2e8f0'">
